Name: Aleksandr Kerensky
Details: The last Commanding General of the Star League Defense Force, Aleksandr Kerensky was responsible for liberating Terra after the coup made by Stephan Amaris, who killed the last First Lord of the Star League, Richard Cameron, and declared himself Emperor of all known space. After the dissolution of the Star League by its Council Lords and unwilling to take sides in the upcoming succession wars, in 2784 Kerensky led the majority of the SLDF away from the Inner Sphere and into exile, in what was called 'Operation Exodus'. Their destination and final fate are unknown.
